<br>
THE ROAD TO HIGHPASS<br>
<br>
Within a couple of weeks, the notice came through from Merani.  We were going to have a meeting of our guild to-be.  I couldn’t wait!<br>
<br>
           “Where is the meeting?”<br>
           “Highpass,” Merani said.  “Can you and Montag be there in 30 minutes?”<br>
<br>
I laughed at her.  Did she not remember the words, ‘Don’t do it, Gar’?  For me, West Karana was a minefield.  And with North Karana beyond it, the plains were the great frontier keeping me from the rest of the world.  <br>
<br>
           “Be there?” I said.  “I don’t know where it is, much less how to survive the trip!”<br>
           “I’ll come and get you.”  <br>
<br>
Montag and I gathered ourselved, and sure enough Merani showed up as she promised.  I invis’d Montag and the two of us ran closely behind Merani, our capable guide.  It was the middle of the night.  Pitch black!  But I still felt safe in the company of my mentor.  Since Merani and I were both trackers, we talked about the many creatures of this dangerous place.  It must have been this conversation that gave her the idea.  She wanted to show us rookies what a Cyclops looked like… Froon and Choon.  <br>
<br>
Was this such a good idea?<br>
<br>
Not sure what happened or why, but for some reason I got left at the bottom of the hill as Merani and Montag crept up to get a peek at the monsters.  Damn this human night vision!  I tried to track them, but it wasn’t working near the hill.  They were gone and I was left in the dark at the cabin.  Hey, at least I had a reference point.  <br>
<br>
So I waited.  I had a bad feeling about this... and I was right.<br>
<br>
Suddenly Merani’s health PLUMMETTED.  My heart started racing.<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “Uh… guys?” I whimpered.<br>
<br>
Merani’s health dived again.  Merani was dying!  And if SHE was dying, Montag and I were rats on a stick! <br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “NOOOOO!” I screamed.<br>
<br>
Here I am, standing alone in the dark, don’t know which way is home and my trusted guide is about to be on the mother of all corpse runs!  Should I just pick a direction and run?  Maybe I’d get lucky and zone… then again maybe I’d trip over that werewolf out there and loose my things forever..<br>
<br>
Then… a miracle.  <br>
<br>
At only a sliver of life, Merani’s health SHOT UP to full!  “RUN!” she screamed.  Luckily, my tracking skill began to return and I found them several meters from the cabin.  We hauled ass and didn’t look back.  I wasn’t THAT curious to see a Cyclops. <br>
<br>
             &quot;Merani, what happened?&quot; I asked.<br>
             &quot;I got too close,&quot; she said.<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “But how did you live?” <br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp “I owe my life to Montag,” she said.  “He used his Lay of Hands.”<br>
<br>
I couldn’t believe it.  My friend Montag!  Saving the life of MY powerful mentor!  HA!<br>
<br>
Was Montag gonna be in the guild?  Oh please.  He had a better shot than me. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=8.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=8.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.eq-arrow-of-light.com/aol/images/boardbuttons/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.threadControl?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http: